</p>
<p>founded&#8221;. He takes note that the AANDC accepted this finding and that it complies with 
</p>
<p>the recommendations made by the Office of the Privacy Commissioner. He looks forward 
</p>
<p>to receiving information once the Canadian Human Rights Tribunal (CHRT) reaches a 
</p>
<p>decision regarding the retaliation proceedings linked to the case.   
