</p>
<p>of Dr. Chandra Kant Raut, which appears to be related to his peaceful advocacy activities 
</p>
<p>and activism and ultimately the exercise of his right to freedom of opinion and expression. 
</p>
<p>He is especially concerned due to the charge of treason that has been brought against Dr. 
