</p>
<p>defender due to comments allegedly made concerning the judicial system could have a 
</p>
<p>negative impact on the possibility of public discussions on critical human rights issues as </p>

<p><b>A/HRC/28/63/Add.1 
</b></p>
<p><b>46</b>  
</p>
<p>well as on the operational space of the human rights defenders to exercise their legitimate 
</p>
