</p>
<p>21/01/2014 
</p>
<p><b> Alleged disproportionate use of force and arbitrary arrest of peaceful 
</b></p>
<p><b>protestors, including journalists and human rights defenders, by Egyptian security 
</b></p>
<p><b>forces. 
</b></p>
